public interface FileConfiguration
extends Configuration
An interface that extends Configuration to get from a file.

Using null for @NotNull argument will cause a NullPointerException.

  • メソッドの詳細

    • load

      boolean load()
      Loads a yaml file.

      If a yaml file is not found, this method will create one.

      戻り値:
      True if the load is successful or false if it is failure.

    • isLoaded

      boolean isLoaded()
      Checks if the file is loaded.
      戻り値:
      True if the file is loaded or false if it is not loaded.

    • reload

      default boolean reload()
      Reload a yaml file.
      戻り値:
      True if the reload is successful or false if it is failure.
      関連項目:
      load()

    • save

      boolean save()
      Save to yaml file.

      If a yaml file is not found, this method will create one.

      戻り値:
      True if the save is successful or false if it is failure.

      Get the path to a yaml file.
